messageBody:
On Monday 11 October 2004 02:44, saji bekal wrote:
> Hi,
>
> Will JUnit work wit old JDKs ? I mean jdk's like 1.2
> or 1.3 versions of JDK ?. Is JUnit depending on assert

'Yes' it will work with older JDKs and 'No' it does not depend on the assert
keyword.

--
Jason Rogers
